Kerry Kennedy has been arrested for driving while under the influence of drugs.

Robert F. Kennedy's daughter, who is the ex-wife of New York Governor Andrew Cuomo, was found slumped at the wheel of her car after a collision in Westchester County, New York this morning.

She crashed her Lexus into a tractor-trailer on Interstate 684 around 8am, according to officials.

The collision comes just two months after her best friend and sister-in-law Mary committed suicide after struggling with alcoholism and drug abuse.

